    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to level 1 or not-assessed per MRL 2 requirements. Experimental validation demonstrates mean relative error of 8.4% against in-vitro hemolysis measurements across five COU operating points. Worst-case operating condition (minimum impeller clearance, 3 L/min, 3500 RPM) identified with RH < 1 relative to predicate device. Model credibility is sufficient to support the intended regulatory submission decision for Class II CPB device tolerance specification.",
